      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean with only a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with regular use, while the interior remains comfortable and free of major wear or tears. Mechanically, the car is solid, starts reliably, and handles well on the road. It represents a great balance for someone looking for a dependable vehicle that still looks sharp and has plenty of life left in it.",
