    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s been kept spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels and drives like it\u2019s brand new, this is definitely the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Swing by and take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
