    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This FD3S RX-7 is a superlative example of Mazda\u2019s rotary engineering. At its heart is a 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged engine, delivering a seamless power band with zero boost leak or hesitation. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 5-speed manual gearbox and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a full refresh of the complex vacuum 'rat's nest' and a cooling system overhaul to mitigate thermal soak. The chassis remains structurally flawless, featuring the original double-wishbone suspension geometry and aluminum control arms for unrivaled kinematic precision. This is a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle with optimal compression across all rotor faces and a completely stock, unmolested configuration.",
      "price": 48500.0,
