    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in true showroom condition. Meticulously maintained and stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage, the exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating\u2014entirely free of swirls, stone chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery still retains its original factory aroma and shows no signs of bolster wear, fading, or creasing. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, documenting a history of rigorous, preventative maintenance performed only by certified specialists. The alloy wheels are pristine with no curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with nearly full tread depth. This car comes with a comprehensive service portfolio, all original keys, and the factory window sticker. It is, quite simply, the finest and most well-preserved example of this model currently available on the market.",
